FTSE 100 Index Little Changed in London as ITV Slides, Randgold Advances

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-03-31T14:20:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/ftse-100-index-little-changed-in-london-as-itv-slides-randgold-advances.html
U.K. stocks swung between gains and
losses, halting the longest stretch of gains for the FTSE 100
Index in six months.  The FTSE 100 was little changed at 5,946.09 at 3:13 p.m. in
 London , after climbing for the previous six days.  ITV Plc paced declining shares, falling 3.9 percent in
London. Randgold Resources Ltd. led advancing shares, rallying
8.3 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah Jones at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net  